ode save to use the three (3) ICONs for Career, one (1) 5-star Coach available for hire in Manager Career, one (1) 5-star Youth Scout for hire in Manager Career and Manager Live challenge content. FC Points will be distributed in 3 equal increments. The initial distribution will be granted with your initial login into the Ultimate Team in the Product, the second distribution will be granted by the end of the subsequent month, and the 3rd distribution will be granted by the end of the following month. You must complete the steps to obtain the initial FC Points distribution by June 15, 2026 to receive all 4,500 (for Nintendo Switch) or 6,000 (for all other platforms) FC Points. If you redeem after September 15, 2026, you will not receive any FC Points. Season 1 Premium Pass will not be available after Season 1 ends; see <a href="https://lapergola-pizzeria.ch/de/games/ea-sports-fc/fc-26/news/pitch-notes-fc26-launch-update" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">lapergola-pizzeria.ch/games/ea-sports-fc/fc-26/news/pitch-notes-fc26-launch-update</a> for more info on Season 1 dates, when available. FC 26 ICON Player Item will be available from September 19, 2025 and will be upgraded to &quot;Champion&quot; version by November 30, 2025; all other Ultimate Edition content will be available from September 26, 2025 unless otherwise noted. All pre-order content for use with one EA account and is non-transferable. Consult your retailer for distribution details. Some content may require gameplay to unlock. Product will be available to download once 7 day early access period begins September 19, 2025 (consumer local time). Early access will not be available if you redeem after September 25, 2025. Pre-order content will not be available if you redeem after September 26, 2026 unless otherwise noted. The Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S versions of the Product give you access to download and play the game on both Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S. The PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 version of the Product will give you access to download and play the game on both PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5. Offer has no cash value and may not be substituted, exchanged, or sold for cash, goods, or services. May not be combined with other offers or prepaid card redeemable for the applicable content unless expressly authorized by EA. Customer is responsible for applicable sales tax. Void where prohibited, taxed, or restricted by law. Internet connection, EA account, acceptance of EA User Agreement (<a href="https://terms.lapergola-pizzeria.ch/" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">terms.lapergola-pizzeria.ch</a>) &amp; Privacy &amp; Cookie Policy (<a href="https://privacy.lapergola-pizzeria.ch/" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">privacy.lapergola-pizzeria.ch</a>), registration with single-use product code, and applicable platform account may be required to play &amp; to access online features, Ultimate Edition content, and pre-order content. Installation of the EA app (<a href="https://lapergola-pizzeria.ch/de/" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">lapergola-pizzeria.ch/ea-app</a>) may be required for the PC product. Age restrictions apply. See <a href="https://o.lapergola-pizzeria.ch/ea/child-access" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">o.lapergola-pizzeria.ch/ea/child-access</a> and applicable platform account for details. Mandatory content updates may be downloaded automatically, require additional storage, incur bandwidth usage fees, &amp; require an additional purchase to access. EA may retire online features with 30-day notice at <a href="https://lapergola-pizzeria.ch/de/service-updates" class="HeadlessButton_container__8o18T TextLink_link__MDSuL">lapergola-pizzeria.ch/service-updates</a>. See final product details at <a href="https://lapergola-p